@AbapCatalog.viewEnhancementCategory: [#NONE]
@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Lojistik Raporu SAS Listesi'
@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
@ObjectModel.usageType:{
    serviceQuality: #X,
    sizeCategory: #S,
    dataClass: #MIXED
}
define view entity YI_NFT_DDL_IMP_LOGIS_PO
  as select from I_PurchaseOrderAPI01     as ekko
    inner join   I_PurchaseOrderItemAPI01 as ekpo on ekpo.PurchaseOrder = ekko.PurchaseOrder
    inner join   ynft_t_t001              as t001 on t001.bsart         = ekko.PurchaseOrderType
    left outer join YI_NFT_DDL_IMP_SHIP_QTY as shipment on shipment.purchaseorder = ekpo.PurchaseOrder
                                                       and shipment.purchaseorderitem = ekpo.PurchaseOrderItem
    left outer join YI_NFT_DDL_IMP_CLEA_QTY_PO as clearence on clearence.purchaseorder = ekpo.PurchaseOrder
                                                       and clearence.purchaseorderitem = ekpo.PurchaseOrderItem 
    left outer join YI_NFT_DDL_IMP_CLEA_GOODS_RECE as GoodsReceipt on GoodsReceipt.purchaseorder = ekpo.PurchaseOrder
                                                                  and GoodsReceipt.purchaseorderitem = ekpo.PurchaseOrderItem                                                                                                             
{
  key ekpo.PurchaseOrder,
  key ekpo.PurchaseOrderItem,
  ekko.PurchaseOrderType,
  ekko.CompanyCode,
  ekko.PurchasingOrganization,
  ekko.PurchasingGroup,
  ekko.PurchaseOrderDate,
  ekko.IncotermsLocation1,
  ekko.IncotermsLocation2,
  ekko.PaymentTerms,
  ekko.Supplier,
  ekpo.Plant,
  ekpo.StorageLocation,
  ekpo.Material,
  ekpo.MaterialGroup,
  ekpo.MaterialType,
  @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure: 'PurchaseOrderQuantityUnit'
  ekpo.OrderQuantity,
  ekpo.PurchaseOrderQuantityUnit,
  @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure: 'PurchaseOrderQuantityUnit'
  case when shipment.quantity is null then ekpo.OrderQuantity else cast( ( ekpo.OrderQuantity - shipment.quantity ) as abap.quan(13,3) ) end as OnOrder, 
  @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure: 'PurchaseOrderQuantityUnit'
  case when clearence.quantity is null then shipment.quantity else cast( ( shipment.quantity - clearence.quantity ) as abap.quan(13,3) ) end as OnRoad,
  @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure: 'PurchaseOrderQuantityUnit'
  case when GoodsReceipt.quantity is null then clearence.quantity else cast( ( clearence.quantity - GoodsReceipt.quantity ) as abap.quan(13,3) ) end as CustomsCleared,
  @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure: 'PurchaseOrderQuantityUnit'
  GoodsReceipt.quantity as GoodsReceipt  
}
